<lb n="0912b17"/><head type="no">No. 560 [Nos. 559, 561]</head>
<lb n="0912b18"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead>佛說老母女六英經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0912b19"/>
<lb n="0912b20"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0912006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（劉）＋宋【元】【明】</note><app n="0912006"><lem>宋</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">劉宋</rdg></app>天竺三<note n="0912007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">藏＋（法師）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0912007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">藏＋（法師）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0912007"><lem>藏</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">藏法師</rdg></app>求那跋陀<note n="0912008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">羅＋（第三）【元】【明】</note><app n="0912008"><lem>羅</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">羅第三</rdg></app>譯</byline>
<lb n="0912b21"/><div1 type="jing"><p><note n="0912009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛為世尊〕－【宮】</note><app n="0912009"><lem>佛為世尊</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>功德巍巍。愍念眾生為之傷悲。
<lb n="0912b22"/>時與弟子大士相追。止處樂音廣有所開。有
<lb n="0912b23"/>一母人貧老<note n="0912010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">傴僂＝惸惸【宮】</note><app n="0912010"><lem>傴僂</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">惸惸</rdg></app>。長跪問佛。五陰六衰<note n="0912011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">會合＝合會【三】【宮】</note><note n="0912011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">會合＝合會【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0912011"><lem>會
<lb n="0912b24"/>合</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">合會</rdg></app>我身悉為是誰。來何所從去何所歸。<note n="0912012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惟願＝母言【三】【宮】</note><note n="0912012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惟願＝母言【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0912012"><lem>惟
<lb n="0912b25"/>願</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">母言</rdg></app>世尊。為我思惟。佛言善哉。宜識<note n="0912013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">其＝是【宮】</note><app n="0912013"><lem>其</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">是</rdg></app><note n="0912014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">幾＝已【三】【宮】</note><note n="0912014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">幾＝已【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0912014"><lem>幾</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">已</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0912b26"/>諸法因緣識之者希。譬如鑽火兩木相揩。火
<lb n="0912b27"/>不從鑽亦不從燧。火出其間赫赫甚<note n="0912015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">輝＝暉【宮】</note><app n="0912015"><lem>輝</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">暉</rdg></app>。還
<lb n="0912b28"/>燒其木木盡消微。亦如<note n="0912016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">搥＝撾【三】【宮】</note><note n="0912016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">搥＝撾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0912016"><lem>搥</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">撾</rdg></app>鼓。其音哀摧聲
<lb n="0912b29"/>不從革。亦不從<note n="0912017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">搥＝椎【三】【宮】</note><note n="0912017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">搥＝椎【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0912017"><lem>搥</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">椎</rdg></app>。諸法如是。因緣相推。<note n="0912018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">亦＝譬【三】【宮】</note><note n="0912018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">亦＝譬【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0912018"><lem>亦</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">譬</rdg></app>
<pb ed="T" id="T14.0560.0912c" n="0912c"/>
<lb n="0912c01"/>如天雨風雲<note n="0912019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">雷電＝電雷【三】【宮】</note><note n="0912019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">雷電＝電雷【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0912019"><lem>雷電</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">電雷</rdg></app>合會作雨。不獨龍威。諸
<lb n="0912c02"/>法如是<note n="0912020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔文〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0912020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔文〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0912020"><lem>文</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>亦如<note n="0912021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">是＋（非）【三】，（作）【宮】</note><note n="0912021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">是＋（非）【宋】【元】【明】，（作）【宮】</note><app n="0912021"><lem>是</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">是非</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">是作</rdg></app>。譬如畫師。調和彩色因
<lb n="0912c03"/>素<note n="0912022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">加＝如【三】【宮】</note><note n="0912022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">加＝如【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0912022"><lem>加</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">如</rdg></app>畫無形不即。皆須緣合非獨一力。母
<lb n="0912c04"/>人聞經。歡<note n="0912023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">喜＝欣【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0912023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">喜＝欣【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0912023"><lem>喜</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">欣</rdg></app>傾側即得法忍。身不疲極。阿
<lb n="0912c05"/>難<note n="0912024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">啟＝披【三】【宮】</note><note n="0912024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">啟＝披【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0912024"><lem>啟</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">披</rdg></app>陳。此何母人。<note n="0912025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">問佛諸＝聞佛說【三】【宮】</note><note n="0912025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">問佛諸＝聞佛說【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0912025"><lem>問佛諸</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">聞佛說</rdg></app>法生死所從。心
<lb n="0912c06"/><note n="0912026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">開意＝意開【三】【宮】</note><note n="0912026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">開意＝意開【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0912026"><lem>開意</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">意開</rdg></app>解即得道真</p>
<lb n="0912c07"/><p>佛語阿難。聽我所言。前過去佛名曰拘<note n="0912027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">樓秦＝留秦佛【三】【宮】</note><note n="0912027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">樓秦＝留秦佛【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0912027"><lem>樓
<lb n="0912c08"/>秦</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">留秦佛</rdg></app>。爾時此母是我之親。我行學道<note n="0912028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">戀＝孿【宮】</note><app n="0912028"><lem>戀</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">孿</rdg></app>閉我
<lb n="0912c09"/>身。憂思<note n="0912029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔不食〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0912029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔不食〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0912029"><lem>不食</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>一日之間。緣<note n="0912030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此＝是【三】【宮】</note><note n="0912030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">此＝是【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0912030"><lem>此</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">是</rdg></app>恩愛。五百
<lb n="0912c10"/>世貧。今我得佛萬福皆臻。眾生無量清淨佛
<lb n="0912c11"/><note n="0912031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">前＝道【三】</note><note n="0912031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">前＝道【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0912031"><lem>前</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">道</rdg></app>。過六十<note n="0912032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">億＝一【三】【宮】</note><note n="0912032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">億＝一【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0912032"><lem>億</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">一</rdg></app>劫當得作佛號薩婆。國<note n="0912033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">名＋（號）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0912033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">名＋（號）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0912033"><lem>名</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">名號</rdg></app>多
<lb n="0912c12"/><note n="0912034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">華＝化【三】【宮】</note><note n="0912034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">華＝化【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0912034"><lem>華</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">化</rdg></app>。劫名禮禪。時人衣<note n="0912035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">食＝服【三】【宮】</note><note n="0912035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">食＝服【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0912035"><lem>食</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">服</rdg></app>如忉利天。各壽一
<lb n="0912c13"/>劫無有<note n="0912036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">苦勤＝勤苦【元】【明】</note><app n="0912036"><lem>苦勤</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">勤苦</rdg></app>。爾時母人天龍夜叉聞佛說法。
<lb n="0912c14"/>皆大歡<app type="＊" source="0912023"><lem>喜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">欣</rdg></app><note n="0912037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔八萬…意〕十一字－【元】【明】</note><app n="0912037" word-count="11"><lem>八萬七千人皆得正真道意</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。禮
<lb n="0912c15"/>佛而去</p>
<lb n="0912c16"/><trailer>佛說老母女六英經</trailer><juan fun="close" n="001"></juan></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>